      <textAnnotation id="sid-12ECF90C-000F-4C60-A1D1-00C62F924445" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>-In R1&amp; R2, Reclassification will be done in ECC or CFin. If in ECC, then replication of same will happen in CFin.
-Detailed process will be covered as part of RICEFW - FPRE0360_CFIN, FPRE0360_IF, FPRE0360_IP
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
